title: 470 Whisper Wind Ln - Founders Village - Awesome Unit!
posting_body: ['Text', 'show contact info', 'to setup a showing!', 'AREA:', 'Castle Rock-', 'Founder Village', 'FEATURES:', 'Gorgeous, brand new construction townhome available now!', 'The property features a spacious floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and a high-end kitchen with a hooded fan.', 'Enjoy the open space, rolling hills and nature just out your back door.', 'Close to I-25 and shopping.', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES:', 'Trash removal, snow removal, landscaping', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All other utilities not above paid by tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 3 bedrooms (upstairs), 2.5 bathrooms (2 bathrooms upstairs, 1/2 bath on the main level)', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Refrigerator, gas stove, dishwasher.', 'LAUNDRY:', 'Washer/dryer hookups.', 'FLOORING: Vinyl flooring on the main level, carpet upstairs, tile in bathrooms, and laundry room.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Central heat and AC.', 'PARKING:', 'Attached 2 car garage.', 'FENCING: n/a.', 'BASEMENT: Unfinished basement.', 'PETS: No pets.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE:', 'Now!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 2 weeks of the property's listed availability date**", 'LEASE TERM:', 'Initial leases are to end April through July of 2023', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
